name: Market Makers
description: Discover the Market Makers - an epic NFT collection by Storm Trade, where trading meets victory. Featuring 5555 unique NFTs representing the iconic Bull, Bear, and Bird, each meticulously hand-drawn by the artist. Every exclusive NFT is given as a reward for the most active Storm.tg users and community members. Holding of NFTs provides you with special bonuses from Storm, such as whitelists for $STORM token. So, who rules the market today?
